New to this zeronet thing, but from what I understand, it really doesn't matter who create this site right? Since there's little to no moderation, users are the one responsible to mute unwanted threads/spam

Or am I missing something? Can mods/owner delete posts before anyone could seed?

>>3bba78d7-f930-4c74-80dd-fa96a3a574cb
>I need to know if I should start getting comfy here.

It's already the most comfy among all alt chan for me, don't get me wrong, this could very well be a honeypot but so is half/full chan at least this is a honeypot without cuckflare and goolag captcha, the 2 things that always bothered me.

Don't wear nostalgia goggle to view 8ch, centralized boards have limits, zeronet is the natural evolution of imageboard technology, I just hope it'll pave the way for future web standard, who knows we might be moving to ipfs in a few years.
